Boeing 757 to Key West in P3Dv5. Everybody survived.
Flight controls: http://www.turtlebeach.com/products/velocity-one-flight

Delta Air Lines flight 1539 service from Atlanta Hartsfield-Jackson Int'l (KATL) to Key West Int'l (KEYW) on the VATSIM network, ATC included. Delta was having equipment shortages and sent a Boeing 757-200 to the 5000ft runway in strong crosswinds. Bold move Cotton.
